<h2>What is this?</h2>
<p>This is the home of HebMorph, an open-source project dedicated to perfecting Hebrew search capabilities. In here you will find all content related to the project and other useful material.</p>
<p>There is also a nice sample search facility built on top of Lucene where you can execute searches with HebMorph, and compare its relevance performance with Lucene's default. For some corpora you can even compare HebMorph to Google search.</p>
<p>New to HebMorph? <a href="http://hebmorph.code972.com/pages/introduction">Click here to get started.</a></p>

